title: Witched Up
description: Keysia has always been a hazard to everyone around her. After just surviving the torture of high school, all she wanted to do was settle down and work on her family’s farm.Everything changes when she finds out she is a witch from a powerful family of Villins and she is to go back to school in another realm to learn of all the ways to being a witch.She struggles at not making a mess of the new academy/college/institute she’s at by a lot.Keysia plus magic equaled a total disaster.Not only this, the mystery of her birth parents’ deaths 16 years ago resurfaces, causing her and her murder investigation team to set out to find the killers. This includes one gorgeous warlock, Emmett Roman Ayers.Emmett ignites something she has never felt before, despite being the cold and stoic warlock he is, adding to the growing pile of mess she has to juggle if she wants to survive Villin Institute.She's also needed to save the entire Realm on top of everything. Imminently…?
author: Lili Jade
